e: none; border-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px" border="0" alt="be_cd2" src="http://members.wpacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/be_cd2.jpg" width="334" height="334" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>What is WP Encyclopedia?</strong></p>\n<p>The <em>WordPress Business Encyclopedia</em> is the most comprehensive training system on the web for making a <strong>WordPress Business Website</strong>. It contains our hugely popular (4000+ students, 70+ five-star reviews) short courses <em>WordPress Essentials for Business</em> and<em> WordPress Theme Selection and Customization</em>, and 6 other modules covering: SEO, Shopping Carts and Payment Systems, Newsletter Management Systems, Social Media Integration, Video Production, along with a reference section covering many important topics such as graphic creation / editing using free tools, moving WordPress websites, the best hosting companies, HTML/CSS quick start guides, and much much more.&#160; </p>\n<p><strong>WP Encyclopedia is in active development through July 2014</strong></p>\n<p>This means you will get all updates through next summer (your access to the 2014 edition will never expire).&#160; What’s more you can get started learning right away with 220 topics and 170 HD videos covering every aspect of creating an attractive, money-making website.&#160; </p>\n<p>There is currently no other course on the internet that covers this range of content (in depth or breadth).&#160;&#160; And it will get even better with courses currently in production including the <em>WordPress eCommerce</em> course and the <em>Plugin Selection course</em>.&#160; The latter will cover all the major categories of plugins, providing recommendations and quick-start configuration videos of our recommended solutions. Gone are the days of choosing WordPress plugins by trial-and-error, while trying to decode documentation that was written for developers.</p>\n<p><strong><a href="http://wpacademy.com/enc/">Grab your copy of WP Encyclopedia 2014 Here</a></strong></p>\n<p>Then enter promo code XMAS (all-caps) at checkout for a $17 discount on the usual $47 price (net $30 to you).&#160; You must act before<u> Wednesday Dec. 18 (midnight EST)</u> to get the discount!</p>\n<p>To your success,</p>\n<p><img title="Marc Beneteau" alt="" src="http://wpacademy.tv/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/marc-full-150x150.jpg" width="150" height="150" /></p>\n<p>Marc Beneteau   <br />”Your Small-Biz Web Technology Mentor”</p>\n<p>The post <a href="http://members.wpacademy.com/2013/12/wp-encyclopedia-on-sale-72-hours-only/">WP Encyclopedia On Sale &ndash; 72 hours only</a> appeared first on <a href="http://members.wpacademy.com">WordPress Training</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:80:"http://members.wpacademy.com/2013/12/wp-encyclopedia-on-sale-72-hours-only/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"Hosting Sale – Last Day";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:59:"http://members.wpacademy.com/2013/12/hosting-sale-last-day/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:68:"http://members.wpacademy.com/2013/12/hosting-sale-las