 permanently lost</p>\n<p>3) Conventional hosts do not support WordPress theme or plugin issues, CSS questions, etc</p>\n<p>4) WordPress sites are inherently slow unless you do something</p>\n<p>Here is your chance to stop worrying about your WordPress sites’ security and performance – while paying just a few dollars more than conventional hosting</p>\n<h3>BLACK FRIDAY SPECIAL (Expires Mon. Dec. 2)</h3>\n<h3>Purchase a year’s Managed WordPress Hosting contract and pay just $10.50 per month annualized!&#160; </h3>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong><a href="https://wpwebsitenow.com/billing/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=3"><strong>Click HERE &gt;&gt;</strong></a>&#160; <br />(Choose yearly billing and enter coupon FRIDAY)</p>\n<p>WP Academy has been offering Managed WordPress Hosting to its own students for years.&#160; We suggest to everyone – and especially beginners – to let their hosting company manage their site’s security and performance.&#160; Most WordPress managed hosting is quite expensive, unfortunately.&#160; </p>\n<p>If you don’t have the fat wallet that would allow you to buy regular managed hosting, and yet want to know your website is taken care of, WP Academy is here to help.&#160; We will support ALL your WordPress issues, AND provide high-performance servers guaranteed 99.9% uptime.&#160; We will give you $100 worth of backup software and we’ll login to your site periodically to make sure it’s working for you (we can actually perform a whole range of security checks and cleanup operations at our semi-yearly security assessment – at <strong>no additional cost</strong>).&#160; </p>\n<p>You must act soon to benefit from this rare discount to our popular hosting service:</p>\n<p><strong>&#160;</strong><a href="https://wpwebsitenow.com/billing/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=3"><strong>Click HERE &gt;&gt;</strong></a>    <br />(Yearly billing, coupon FRIDAY)</p>\n<p>The coupon expires <u>MONDAY DEC. 02 AT MIDNIGHT</u></p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: if you are new to hosting you