 originally offered at $147, then a few days ago it went down to $47 Retail, and now – for a limited time –<em> I am making it available to my loyal subscribers for just $30.</em></p>\n<p><strong>&gt;&gt; <a href="http://wpacademy.com/enc/"><strong>Get WP Encyclopedia for just $30 here</strong></a> &lt;&lt;</strong><br />\n(Use promo code LOYAL at checkout before Tuesday Nov. 12)</p>\n<h3>What do you get with WP Encyclopedia 2014?</h3>\n<p>WP Encyclopedia is designed as a comprehensive reference and training guide for creating a <strong>business website or blog</strong>.  it is the <span style="text-decoration: underline;">only</span> such resource of its kind in the world, providing resources and quick start videos on <span style="text-decoration: underline;">every aspect</span> of creating an attractive, lead-generating, money-making website.  This includes – in addition to our hugely popular <em>WordPress Essentials for Business</em> and <em>Theme Selection courses</em> &#8212; chapters on SEO, Shopping carts &amp; Membership Systems, Social Media integration, Newsletter integration, Online Video Production, and much more.</p>\n<p>Quite simply, there is no other course on the internet that that gives you so much practical and directly actionable information in such a brief time to create an effective, business-oriented website.  WP Encyclopedia was created for my students, and has been field-tested with hundreds (or thousands) of WordPress websites over the last 4 years.</p>\n<p>Check out the feature tour videos here:</p>\n<p><a href="http://wpacademy.com/enc/"><img style="background-image: none; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border: 0px;" title="is-wpencyclopedia-for-you" alt="is-wpencyclopedia-for-you" src="http://members.wpacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/is-wpencyclopedia-for-you.jpg" width="244" height="183" border="0" /></a></p>\n<p>(and then donate to the project and save $17 with coupon LOYAL)</p>\n<h3>What about plugins, themes and other commercial services – do you cover that?</h3>\n<p>Glad you asked.  As you know, the power of WordPress sits mostly in the plugins and themes that are available for it.  But how to select the best plugins and themes for your site, other than time-consuming and painful research and trial &amp; error?</p>\n<p>WP Encyclopedia already has in-depth feature tours and quick-start videos covering 7 major free and commercial theme families.  We are actively working on our next addition to WP Encyclopedia, which is the Plugin Selection course.  This will be published in January and will include reviews, feature tours and quick-configuration videos for the most popular and functional WordPress plugins by category.  Like everything else in WP Encyclopedia, this will be searchable.  This function alone will save you hours of work and headaches.</p>\n<p>But, we need your help to make this happen.</p>\n<p><strong>&gt;&gt; <a href="http://wpacademy.com/enc/"><strong>Donate to the WP Encyclopedia Project</strong></a> &lt;&lt; </strong><br />\n(Remember coupon LOYAL gives you $17 off retail – but the coupon is only good until <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Tuesday Nov. 12 at midnight</span>)</p>\n<p>PS: Did you miss yesterday’s mail about our upcoming live training and coaching events this week?  Check it <a href="http://members.wpacademy.com/ecommerce-store-in-45-minutes-and-other-free-training-this-week.htm">HERE</a> – its FREE</p>\n<p>PPS: If it’s not the right time for you to help us out, please share the <a href="http://wpacademy.com/enc/">campaign page</a> with your friends and followers!</p>\n<p>To Your Success,</p>\n<p>Marc Beneteau<br />\n”Your Small-Biz Web Technology Mentor”<br />\n<img style="background-image: none; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border: 0px;" title="marc-portrait-final-crop2" alt="marc-portrait-final-crop2" src="http://members.wpacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/marc-portrait-final-crop2.jpg" width="100" height="100" border="0" /></p>\n<p>The post <a href="http://members.wpacademy.com/2013/11/wp-encyclopedia-on-sale-through-tuesday-1112/">WP Encyclopedia on sale through Tuesday 11/12</a> appeared first on <a href="http://members.wpacademy.com">WordPress Training</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:87:"http://members.wpacademy.com/2013/11/wp-encyclopedia-on-sale-through-tuesday-1112/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}}s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:3:{s:4:"href";s:48:"http://members.wpacademy.com/category/news/feed/";s:3:"rel";s:4:"self";s:4:"type";s:19:"application/rss+xml";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:44:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/";a:2:{s:12:"updatePeriod";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"hourly";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:15:"updateFrequency";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"1";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:"type";i:128;s:7:"headers";a:10:{s:4:"date";s:29:"Tue, 21 Jan 2014 23:15:54 GMT";s:6:"server";s:9:"LiteSpeed";s:10:"connection";s:5:"close";s:12:"x-powered-by";s:10:"PHP/5.4.19";s:10:"set-cookie";a:5:{i:0;s:55:"wlmdebug=deleted; expires=Thu, 01-Jan-1970 00:00:01 GMT";i:1;s:210:"wc_session_cookie_d0fb3bf6a09f702cdfb97e4d2c564710=g6jIOTzivPXnO7zAH2vrJqfYgNkh54KH%7C%7C1390518953%7C%7C1390515353%7C%7C80e5c257956bd6